        "Title": "The Devil&apos;s Due",
        "Description": "The Devil&apos;s Own has returned to Colorado, sent forth to bring fire and brimstone to the sinners of the world.\r\rThe Devil has dispatched you, 47, to drag these four souls down into his lake of fire. There are several gasoline drums scattered throughout the farm, use them to do the Devil&apos;s work.\r\rThe Devil collects his due. Good luck, 47.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Casetros.",
